name: iPhone 12
description: The iPhone 12 is a flagship smartphone from Apple with a 6.1-inch Super Retina XDR display, A14 Bionic chip, and 5G connectivity.

name: Smart Watch
description: This smartwatch features a 1.3-inch color display, heart rate monitoring, sleep tracking, and notification alerts.

name: Wireless Headphones
description: These wireless headphones feature active noise cancellation, up to 30 hours of battery life, and support for Siri and Google Assistant.
